Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.37,0:01:04.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶  我们要去珊迪家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.37,0:01:04.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, we're going to Sandy's house
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.03,0:01:06.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要比你先到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.03,0:01:06.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to beat you there
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.16,0:01:07.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给树捂热乎点  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.16,0:01:07.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep the tree warm, Sandy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.63,0:01:13.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(660,826)}禁止入内
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.53,0:01:14.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.53,0:01:14.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.42,0:01:16.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.42,0:01:16.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.54,0:01:17.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干嘛挂牌子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.54,0:01:17.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what's with the sign
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.10,0:01:21.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看  她上美食频道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.10,0:01:21.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, she's on The Eating Channel
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.90,0:01:25.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.90,0:01:25.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.47,0:01:28.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果你看到了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.47,0:01:28.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If y'all are watching this
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.84,0:01:31.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就表示我过冬睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.84,0:01:31.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that means I'm asleep for the winter
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.45,0:01:34.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,此时的睡眠就叫做冬眠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.45,0:01:34.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This sleep is called hibernation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.32,0:01:34.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1040,634)}冬眠
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.57,0:01:38.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冬眠期间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.57,0:01:38.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,During hibernation
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.02,0:01:40.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,动物们都很不愿意突然被吵醒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.02,0:01:40.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,animals don't like to be woken up
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.12,0:01:42.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以请勿打扰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:42.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So do not disturb
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.90,0:01:45.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说的就是你  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.90,0:01:45.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That means you, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.02,0:01:47.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好戴上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.02,0:01:47.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We better put these on
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.77,0:01:49.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不必了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.77,0:01:49.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never mind, Pat
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.02,0:01:50.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪说不要进去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:50.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy said not to come in
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.46,0:01:52.38,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1112,456)}排水
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.67,0:01:51.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们还是开溜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.67,0:01:51.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's amscray
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.39,0:01:54.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你什么时候才学得会  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.39,0:01:54.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When are you going to learn, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.87,0:01:56.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不的意思就是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.87,0:01:56.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"No" means "yes"
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.55,0:01:57.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:01:57.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, listen
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.72,0:01:59.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得多少次才能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.72,0:01:59.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how many times do we have to
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.26,0:02:01.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:01.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, look at this
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.45,0:02:11.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.45,0:02:11.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is this stuff?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.67,0:02:14.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是辽阔梦幻的仙境
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.67,0:02:14.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a vast, swirling wonderland
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.25,0:02:16.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,充满洁白闪耀的好景
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.25,0:02:16.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of sparkling white pleasure
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.97,0:02:18.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来充实你的感官
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.97,0:02:18.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let it fill your senses
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.72,0:02:22.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尽享层层叠叠  松软如枕的舒爽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.72,0:02:20.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with cascading, fluffy pillows
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.62,0:02:22.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of excitement and comfort
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.52,0:02:24.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,体验从未有过的怡情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.52,0:02:24.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as you've never felt before
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.75,0:02:26.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哇  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.75,0:02:26.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wow, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.60,0:02:27.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好文采
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.60,0:02:27.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was beautiful
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.91,0:02:28.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.91,0:02:28.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.58,0:02:30.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚在念这张糖果包装纸  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:30.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was just reading this candy wrapper, see?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.28,0:02:34.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.28,0:02:34.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.00,0:02:35.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把头盔戴回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:35.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put your helmet back on
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.47,0:02:38.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪家里没有水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.47,0:02:38.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know there's no water at Sandy's house
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.09,0:02:39.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.09,0:02:39.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's okay, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.97,0:02:41.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这东西就是水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:41.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This stuff is water
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.95,0:02:42.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.95,0:02:42.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.01,0:02:45.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来你说的对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:45.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.65,0:02:47.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脱掉不会有事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.65,0:02:47.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's okay here
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.29,0:02:48.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脱掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.29,0:02:48.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take it off
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.92,0:02:50.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没人看的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:50.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one's looking
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.85,0:03:01.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你听见没
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.85,0:03:01.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, did you hear that?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.24,0:03:04.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该是从珊迪的树里面传来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:04.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think it came from up in Sandy's tree
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.07,0:03:08.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好一棵累垮的树
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.07,0:03:08.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is one tired tree
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.03,0:03:10.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.03,0:03:10.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's check it out
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.32,0:03:14.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看珊迪的床上有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.32,0:03:14.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look what's in Sandy's bed
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.12,0:03:18.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,像个充了太多气的珊迪娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.12,0:03:18.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like an overinflated Sandy doll
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.17,0:03:20.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这东西好像就是珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:20.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think this thing is Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.30,0:03:21.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冬眠一定就是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:21.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hibernation must mean
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.92,0:03:23.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美容觉的反义词
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.92,0:03:23.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the opposite of beauty sleep
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.80,0:03:30.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经受够你肮脏的勾当了  坏蛋丹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.80,0:03:30.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of your dastardly deeds, Dirty Dan
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.38,0:03:34.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要逮到你和你同伙  钉子头拉里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.38,0:03:34.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna get you and your partner, Pinhead Larry
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.48,0:03:35.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然我就不叫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:35.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or my name ain't
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.87,0:03:38.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,警长珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.87,0:03:38.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sheriff Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.17,0:03:42.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她一定是梦见了德克萨斯的罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.17,0:03:42.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She must be dreaming about Texas outlaws
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.87,0:03:47.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:47.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look out, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.35,0:03:49.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是坏蛋丹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.35,0:03:49.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Dirty Dan
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.32,0:03:52.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要逮到你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:52.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna catch you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.53,0:03:56.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用纳税人的钱把你关进牢里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.53,0:03:56.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and throw in jail at taxpayers' expense
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.33,0:03:59.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好跑快点  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.33,0:03:59.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You better run faster, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.35,0:04:00.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  我就快逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.35,0:04:00.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm getting away
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.89,0:04:01.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跑快点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.89,0:04:01.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run faster
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.90,0:04:03.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快啊  我们就快上出租车了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:03.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry, we're getting in a taxi
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.75,0:04:04.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.75,0:04:04.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Faster, faster
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.63,0:04:07.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要逮到你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.63,0:04:07.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll get you two
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.92,0:04:10.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们就是纯粹的邪恶化身
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.92,0:04:10.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're nothing but pure evil
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.27,0:04:13.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就跟报纸上的漫画一个样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:13.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just like newspaper comics
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.87,0:04:18.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.87,0:04:18.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.15,0:04:19.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别再打扰人家了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:19.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We shouldn't disturb her anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.94,0:04:21.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不叫打扰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:21.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not disturbing
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.78,0:04:23.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这才叫打扰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:23.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is disturbing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:23.52,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(810,920)}膈 应
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.57,0:04:28.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:28.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, there, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.32,0:04:32.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我叫派大背
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.32,0:04:32.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My name is Patback
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.90,0:04:34.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实看着就膈应
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.90,0:04:34.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is really disturbing
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.82,0:04:43.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:43.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.43,0:04:53.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跑快点  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:53.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Faster, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.56,0:04:54.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她快追上我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:54.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's gaining on us
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.77,0:04:56.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:56.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, no
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.17,0:04:56.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.17,0:04:56.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.12,0:04:59.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我警告过你了  坏蛋丹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.12,0:04:59.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I warned you, Dirty Dan
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.40,0:05:02.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在你要被我狠狠揍一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:02.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now you just crossed the border into Hurtville
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.87,0:05:04.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.87,0:05:04.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, it's us
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.47,0:05:06.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你朋友海绵宝宝和派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:06.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your friends SpongeBob and Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.80,0:05:07.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你了  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:07.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.69,0:05:09.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没钱去干洗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.69,0:05:09.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't afford dry cleaning
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.49,0:05:15.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要剥了你们皮  做成六码的靴子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:15.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gonna skin ya and make a pair of size six boots
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.05,0:05:22.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,玩完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:22.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fun's over
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.36,0:05:25.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝对不能又把她吵醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.36,0:05:25.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We sure don't want to wake her up again
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.82,0:05:27.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可惜我们身上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:27.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too bad we don't have
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.53,0:05:29.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有耳塞可以帮她戴上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.53,0:05:29.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,any earplugs to put on her
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.47,0:05:32.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就只有肚脐眼里面的绒毛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:32.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, all's I got is this belly button lint
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.42,0:05:37.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.42,0:05:37.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, Pat
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.72,0:05:43.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要扒了你们胳膊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.72,0:05:43.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna rip your arms off
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.82,0:05:45.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有煎饼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:45.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and flapjacks
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.07,0:05:48.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样应该就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:48.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that ought to work
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.24,0:05:50.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  有没有用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:50.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sandy, does it work?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.55,0:05:59.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  如果听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:05:59.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sandy, if you can't hear us
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.80,0:06:01.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就别说话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.80,0:06:01.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,don't say anything
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.70,0:06:03.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.70,0:06:03.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.97,0:06:05.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.97,0:06:05.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't wake up
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.51,0:06:11.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  警长珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:11.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you later, Sheriff Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.17,0:06:17.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你被捕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.17,0:06:17.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're under arrest
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.22,0:06:19.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你逮不到我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.22,0:06:19.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll never catch me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.52,0:06:27.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样不公平
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.52,0:06:27.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not fair
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.91,0:06:30.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,牛仔可买不起大炮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.91,0:06:30.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cowboys couldn't afford cannons
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.42,0:06:32.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,牛仔也买不起客货两用车
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.42,0:06:32.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They couldn't afford station wagons, either
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.78,0:06:34.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,车身面板不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:34.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice paneling
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.99,0:06:37.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  钉子头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:37.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, Pinhead
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.22,0:06:39.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的死期到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.22,0:06:39.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your time is up
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.29,0:06:41.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你叫谁钉子头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:41.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who you calling Pinhead?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.72,0:06:43.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要当坏蛋丹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.72,0:06:43.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to be Dirty Dan
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.61,0:06:45.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你凭什么觉得你能当坏蛋丹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.61,0:06:45.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What makes you think you can be Dirty Dan?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.96,0:06:47.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我又坏又脏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:47.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm dirty
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.97,0:06:49.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才是坏蛋丹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:49.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd say I'm Dirty Dan
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.60,0:06:53.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才是坏蛋丹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:53.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd say I'm Dirty Dan
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.62,0:06:56.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才是坏蛋丹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.62,0:06:56.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd say I'm Dirty Dan
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.31,0:06:58.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是坏蛋丹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:58.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Dirty Dan
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.89,0:07:00.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是坏蛋丹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:00.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Dirty Dan
