Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.65,0:07:15.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Dirty Dan
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.99,0:07:17.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大喊大叫会害你没
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:17.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Screaming will get you no
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.80,0:07:27.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个谁才是坏蛋丹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:27.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Which one of you fellers is the real Dirty Dan?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.05,0:07:29.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:29.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.13,0:07:33.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:33.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.40,0:07:35.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,辣鸡翅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:35.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hot wings
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.80,0:07:39.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  钉子头拉里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:39.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Pinhead Larry
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.25,0:07:41.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到你受死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:41.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now you get yours
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.24,0:07:47.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钉子头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.24,0:07:47.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pinhead
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.08,0:08:05.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要为你犯的罪付出代价  钉子头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:05.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now you're gonna pay for those crimes, Pinhead
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.39,0:08:07.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  退后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.39,0:08:07.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, stand back
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.92,0:08:09.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我警告你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:09.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm warning ya
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.59,0:08:15.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  我警告过你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:15.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, I warned ya
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.92,0:08:17.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你赢了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.92,0:08:17.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you win?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.82,0:08:21.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:21.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:40.29,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(662,352)}坏蛋丹                   钉子头拉里
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.47,0:08:34.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:34.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.56,0:08:35.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来当坏蛋丹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.56,0:08:35.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you can be Dirty Dan
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.84,0:08:37.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只想当派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:37.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just want to be Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.47,0:08:38.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们快出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.47,0:08:38.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.53,0:08:40.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免得珊迪又突然醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:40.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,before Sandy wakes up again
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.48,0:08:50.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.48,0:08:50.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.48,0:08:51.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,门特别滑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.48,0:08:51.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but the door is slippery
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.78,0:08:53.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冻住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:53.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's frozen shut
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.20,0:08:54.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.20,0:08:54.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me have a try
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.60,0:08:59.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,芝麻开门
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.60,0:08:59.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Open, Sesame
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.02,0:09:01.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经尽力了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:01.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I've done all I can do
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.17,0:09:03.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我们就被困在这了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.17,0:09:03.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then we're stuck in here
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.82,0:09:05.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大门解冻才能出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.82,0:09:05.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,until the door thaws
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.07,0:09:07.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得等到春天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.07,0:09:07.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in spring
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.48,0:09:08.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.48,0:09:08.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.07,0:09:12.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,春天到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:12.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is it spring yet?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.94,0:09:14.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:14.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,N-n-no
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.09,0:09:18.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都冷得打哆嗦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:18.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm so c-c-cold that I'm shivering
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.82,0:09:25.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都冷得能拿鼻涕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:25.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I-I'm so cold that I can use my nose drippings
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.18,0:09:26.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当筷子用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.18,0:09:26.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as a pair of chopsticks
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.49,0:09:29.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我冷得
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.49,0:09:29.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I-I'm so c-cold that
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.90,0:09:32.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都打哆嗦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:32.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm shivering
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.85,0:09:35.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许我们该烧个火
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.85,0:09:35.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should build a fire
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.46,0:09:36.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.46,0:09:36.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.57,0:09:39.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烧珊迪树上的树皮好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.57,0:09:39.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll burn the bark from Sandy's tree
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.50,0:09:43.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等我把你解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.50,0:09:43.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're gonna be wearing an iron lung
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.32,0:09:45.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你必戴人工呼吸器  钉子头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:45.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when I'm through with you, Pinhead
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.36,0:09:50.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,火生不起来  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.36,0:09:50.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The fire's not going to happen, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.82,0:09:52.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:52.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't get it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.12,0:09:55.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪每年咋撑得过这么恶劣的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.12,0:09:52.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How does Sandy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.75,0:09:55.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,survive these intense conditions every year?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.67,0:09:57.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能因为是她直接无视了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:09:57.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe she just ignores it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.49,0:09:59.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:09:59.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.60,0:10:01.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.60,0:10:01.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.22,0:10:03.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能因为她的毛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.22,0:10:03.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's her fur
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.07,0:10:06.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.07,0:10:06.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.27,0:10:12.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看那堆暖和的毛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.27,0:10:12.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at all that warm, toasty fur
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.71,0:10:16.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就好像是长毛的金矿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:16.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's like a gold mine, but with fur
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.05,0:10:17.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.05,0:10:17.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Carefully
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.20,0:10:21.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.20,0:10:21.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Carefully
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.20,0:10:22.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,动作快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:22.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, do it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.06,0:10:23.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都冷死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.06,0:10:23.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm freezing here
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.09,0:10:23.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.09,0:10:23.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, all right
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.75,0:10:24.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,稍安勿躁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:24.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,hang on a second
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.30,0:10:30.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这么多应该够吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:30.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That should be enough, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.75,0:10:32.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我是大男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:32.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sponge, I'm a big man
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.18,0:10:35.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,特别大个的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.18,0:10:35.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A big, big man
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.61,0:10:38.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来我一生已经过完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.61,0:10:38.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I've lived a full life
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.70,0:10:45.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你扒得也太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:45.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is taking too long
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.35,0:10:47.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在就要温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.35,0:10:47.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want the warm now
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.49,0:10:48.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.49,0:10:48.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pat, no
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.00,0:10:54.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你疯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:54.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pat, are you crazy?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.75,0:10:55.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:55.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.55,0:10:56.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我暖和了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:56.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm warm
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.45,0:11:00.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那卷胶带给我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.45,0:11:00.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me see that roll of tape
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.20,0:11:19.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她的毛真的好给力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:19.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Man, that fur really hits the spot
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.42,0:11:21.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胳肢窝再也不会受冻了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.42,0:11:21.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more frozen armpits
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.18,0:11:25.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一字眉山羊胡组合大有奇效
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.18,0:11:25.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And this eyebrow/goatee combo works like a charm
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.60,0:11:27.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我们最好的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:27.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This the best idea we've ever had
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.87,0:11:29.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:29.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You said it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.24,0:11:32.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好度过最久最冷的冬天了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.24,0:11:32.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready for the longest, coldest winter ever
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.90,0:11:35.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:35.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bring it on
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.20,0:11:40.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,春天了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.20,0:11:40.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spring?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.26,0:11:44.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经春天了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.26,0:11:44.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spring already
Dialogue: 1,0:11:46.74,0:11:47.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真该死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.74,0:11:47.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tartar sauce
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.71,0:11:49.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,锁还冻着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.71,0:11:49.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The lock is still frozen
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.42,0:11:53.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我等不及要出去暖暖身上的毛了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.42,0:11:53.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I sure can't wait to get outside and warm my fur
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.73,0:11:59.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看啊  是海绵宝宝跟派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:11:59.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, look, it's SpongeBob and Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.08,0:12:03.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:03.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, guys
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.82,0:12:18.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:18.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.32,0:12:20.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,松鼠型脱毛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:20.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squirrel pattern baldness
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.06,0:12:21.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在小型哺乳动物当中很常见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:21.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is quite common in small mammals
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.05,0:12:24.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:24.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.92,0:12:26.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.92,0:12:26.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.24,0:12:28.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你放心  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:28.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.55,0:12:29.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们会帮你解决的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.55,0:12:29.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got you covered
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.55,0:12:29.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(846,920)}盖 好
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.47,0:12:35.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不要再来点柠檬水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.47,0:12:35.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More lemonade, boys?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.77,0:12:37.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:37.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.79,0:12:40.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,春天真美好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.79,0:12:40.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spring sure is lovely
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:44.45,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(357,346)}被抛弃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:46.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19\pos(442,410)}导演
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:49.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:47.99,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19\pos(412,716)}分镜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:47.99,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19\pos(266,406)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:49.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz18.27\pos(416,284)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:51.91,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(318,342)\frz18.95}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:51.91,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(476,682)\frz21.2}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:51.91,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.68,0:13:00.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到你了  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.68,0:13:00.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got you now, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.10,0:13:03.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓到了  你当鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:03.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tag, you're it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.89,0:13:09.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗肯定不会发现我在这
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:09.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary will never find me here
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.47,0:13:14.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.47,0:13:14.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tag
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.60,0:13:16.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我当鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:16.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I'm it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.50,0:13:24.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:24.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.80,0:13:25.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:25.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.97,0:13:27.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟小蜗在玩抓人游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.97,0:13:27.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary and I are playing tag
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.62,0:13:28.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要一起来玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:28.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You want to join us?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.57,0:13:30.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊  当然要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:30.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, would I?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.19,0:13:32.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.19,0:13:32.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.40,0:13:33.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:33.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tag
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.95,0:13:35.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你当鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:35.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.42,0:13:38.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我当鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.42,0:13:38.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.35,0:13:42.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓到了  你当鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:42.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tag, you're it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.55,0:13:43.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:43.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I win
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.22,0:13:48.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:48.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's with Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.67,0:13:50.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,声音跟汽船似的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.67,0:13:50.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He sounds like a motorboat
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.20,0:13:55.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那只是蜗牛表示喜欢的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:55.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's just a snail's way of saying he likes you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.68,0:13:57.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好痒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.68,0:13:57.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tickles
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.23,0:14:12.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来现在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.23,0:14:12.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it's time
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.72,0:14:14.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟小蜗该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:14.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for me and the Gar Bear to get going
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.80,0:14:16.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.80,0:14:16.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.10,0:14:18.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  我等不及要去睡觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.10,0:14:18.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, I can't wait to hit the hay
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.31,0:14:20.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你呢  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.31,0:14:20.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about you, Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.02,0:14:21.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.02,0:14:21.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.10,0:14:22.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.10,0:14:22.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.84,0:14:25.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刷刷刷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:25.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Brush, brush, brush
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.80,0:14:27.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你看到小蜗了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:27.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick, have you seen Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.65,0:14:28.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刷刷刷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.65,0:14:28.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Brush, brush, brush
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.08,0:14:31.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到处都要刷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.08,0:14:31.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Brushing everywhere
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.68,0:14:33.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:33.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.48,0:14:35.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗在这
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.48,0:14:35.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here he is
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.68,0:14:38.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:38.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.75,0:14:40.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让派大星好好睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:40.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got to let Patrick go to sleep
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.64,0:14:42.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不介意  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.64,0:14:42.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't mind, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.31,0:14:43.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说实话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:43.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In fact
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.31,0:14:46.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然你今晚就让小蜗来我家睡好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.31,0:14:46.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,why don't you let Gary sleep over at my house tonight?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.92,0:14:48.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是个好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.92,0:14:48.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a great idea
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.24,0:14:50.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来过夜  好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:50.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A sleep-over, oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.27,0:14:52.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定会特别棒的  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.27,0:14:52.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is going to be great, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.07,0:14:55.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以通宵看恐怖电影
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:55.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can stay up till dawn and watch scary movies
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.46,0:14:57.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃爆米花  玩桌游
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.46,0:14:57.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and eat popcorn and play board games
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.16,0:15:00.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:00.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is great
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.87,0:15:05.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我全海洋最好的两个朋友一起过夜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:05.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My two best friends in the whole sea having a sleep-over
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.87,0:15:07.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后一起搭纸牌屋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.87,0:15:07.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And then we'll make a house of cards
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.11,0:15:09.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后一起看漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.11,0:15:09.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and then we'll read some comic books
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.30,0:15:11.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  你们好好去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:11.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, you guys have a good time
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.31,0:15:12.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明天再见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:12.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll see you tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.02,0:15:26.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:26.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm awake
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.05,0:15:28.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.05,0:15:28.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.57,0:15:31.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,昨天过夜怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:31.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys, how was the sleep-over?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.41,0:15:32.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可棒了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:32.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.60,0:15:33.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.60,0:15:33.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch this
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.94,0:15:37.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我走到哪小蜗就跟到哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.94,0:15:37.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No matter where I go, Gary follows
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.65,0:15:51.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看到没
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.65,0:15:51.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.82,0:15:52.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.82,0:15:52.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.65,0:15:54.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来抓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.65,0:15:54.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Try and catch
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.92,0:15:56.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.92,0:15:56.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.38,0:16:00.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很棒啊  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.38,0:16:00.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't this great, Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.12,0:16:03.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我到处跑  你来追我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.12,0:16:03.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me running around and you chasing me
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.73,0:16:05.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都没在追我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:05.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not chasing me
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.19,0:16:07.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:07.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.07,0:16:08.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们换另外一个游戏玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:08.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go play a different game
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.90,0:16:16.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心  我就在你前面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:16.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look out, I'm right in front of you
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.40,0:16:18.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.40,0:16:18.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with me?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.77,0:16:20.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冒犯到人家了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:20.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do I offend?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.41,0:16:28.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.41,0:16:28.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.56,0:16:29.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗你看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.56,0:16:29.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, look
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.68,0:16:31.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你最爱的球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:31.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's your favorite ball
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.42,0:16:39.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:39.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.82,0:16:40.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.82,0:16:40.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.81,0:16:42.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(660,236)}蜗薄荷
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.81,0:16:41.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蜗薄荷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.81,0:16:41.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Snail-nip
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.13,0:16:49.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.13,0:16:49.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.82,0:16:50.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  救命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:50.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, help
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.85,0:16:51.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.85,0:16:51.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help me
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.00,0:16:53.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的海神王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:53.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Merciful Neptune
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.68,0:16:56.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我关窗夹到头了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.68,0:16:56.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I closed the window on my head
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.83,0:17:01.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  都够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.83,0:17:01.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, that's it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.94,0:17:09.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  不准你再胡闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.94,0:17:09.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, you stop this foolishness right now
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.90,0:17:14.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蜗牛小蜗  我问话你就必须回话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:14.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary the Snail, answer me when I'm talking to you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.65,0:17:16.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.65,0:17:16.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.25,0:17:17.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.25,0:17:17.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's it, mister
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.42,0:17:19.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你马上跟我回家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.42,0:17:19.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are coming home with me right this instant
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.82,0:17:23.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟派大星说再见  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.82,0:17:23.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say good-bye to Patrick, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.27,0:17:28.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,慢着  生气爸妈宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:28.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there, DadMom AngryPants
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.20,0:17:29.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你那是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.20,0:17:29.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.62,0:17:30.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.62,0:17:30.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.87,0:17:34.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我知道小蜗心里清楚要跟谁走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.87,0:17:34.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I do know Gary knows who he wants to go with
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.02,0:17:37.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,建议你现在给我放下小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:37.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, I suggest you put him down
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.32,0:17:39.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,由小蜗自己来选择
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:39.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and let him choose
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.25,0:17:41.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  但我想提醒一下小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:41.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fine, but I would like to remind him
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.86,0:17:44.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁整天供小蜗吃供小蜗住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.86,0:17:44.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who it was that fed him and housed him
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.45,0:17:46.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在小蜗生病时守在小蜗床边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:46.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and sat at his bedside when he was sick
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.75,0:17:49.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还在眼睛疼的时候帮忙按摩眼柄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:49.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and massaged his eyestalks when his eyes were sore
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.00,0:17:50.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:50.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.93,0:17:52.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去证明给他看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.93,0:17:52.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,go ahead, show him
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.45,0:17:53.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.45,0:17:53.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.26,0:17:53.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来我这边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:53.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,come to me
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.92,0:17:55.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快啊快啊  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.92,0:17:55.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.75,0:17:56.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.75,0:17:56.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.35,0:17:57.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到这来  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.35,0:17:57.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,come here, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.77,0:17:58.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走错了  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.77,0:17:58.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wrong way, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.59,0:17:59.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  快调头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:17:59.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,G-Gary, turn around
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.91,0:18:00.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  调头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:00.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, turn around
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.80,0:18:01.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:01.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, no
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.72,0:18:03.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:03.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, no, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.37,0:18:04.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别过去  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.37,0:18:04.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, don't do it, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.56,0:18:06.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:06.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.31,0:18:08.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:08.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, well, well
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.36,0:18:11.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来答案揭晓了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:11.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess that answers that question
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.45,0:18:13.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.45,0:18:13.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So long, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.02,0:18:15.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟小蜗有事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.02,0:18:15.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary and me got stuff to do
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.65,0:18:17.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:17.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, fine
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.70,0:18:19.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果你就这样谢我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:19.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If that's the way you want to thank me
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.12,0:18:21.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢我为你做的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:21.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for all that I've done
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:24.70,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(746,890)}小蜗
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.68,0:18:29.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来你不肯回来了  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.68,0:18:29.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess you're not coming back, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.30,0:18:33.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不需要小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.30,0:18:33.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't need Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.32,0:18:35.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再找一只宠物好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.32,0:18:35.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just find another pet
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.00,0:18:37.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  肯定比小蜗强
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:37.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it will be better than Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.60,0:18:38.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要养一只
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.60,0:18:38.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get a pet
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.85,0:18:41.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会跟我最好的朋友跑路的宠物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.85,0:18:41.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who won't go off with my best friend
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.18,0:18:47.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:47.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, guys
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.72,0:18:50.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我的新朋友雷克斯打个招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.72,0:18:50.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say hello to my new pal Rex
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.79,0:18:53.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它不仅忠诚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:53.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not only is he loyal
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.25,0:18:54.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还会听我话做动作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:54.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but he knows tricks, too
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.78,0:18:56.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好看好好学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:18:56.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch and learn
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.07,0:18:58.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坐下  雷克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:18:58.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sit, Rex, sit
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.55,0:19:02.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,翻滚  雷克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.55,0:19:02.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Roll over, Rex, roll over
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.42,0:19:05.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要动  雷克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.42,0:19:05.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now stay, Rex, stay
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.19,0:19:08.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,乖虫虫  雷克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.19,0:19:08.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good boy, Rex
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.15,0:19:09.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁是乖虫虫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.15,0:19:09.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's a good boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.01,0:19:11.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁是乖虫虫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:11.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's a good boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.67,0:19:13.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁是乖虫虫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.67,0:19:13.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's a good boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.60,0:19:21.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很高兴我们分道扬镳了  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.60,0:19:21.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sure glad we went our separate ways, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.30,0:19:23.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虫子才是适合我的宠物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.30,0:19:23.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A worm really is the pet for me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.99,0:19:26.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,忠诚  又值得信任
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.99,0:19:26.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So loyal, so trusting
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.65,0:19:28.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在我身边不离不弃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.65,0:19:28.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Always by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:33.19,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1062,280)}公交站
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.66,0:19:36.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁稀罕虫子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.66,0:19:36.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who needs worms anyway?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.70,0:19:39.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎到家  新任好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.70,0:19:39.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, newest best friend
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.23,0:19:41.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出来吧  别害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.23,0:19:41.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on out, don't be shy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.47,0:19:47.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你让我想起了我曾经认识过的某位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.47,0:19:47.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You remind me of someone I once knew
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.50,0:19:49.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.50,0:19:49.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A certain someone whose name
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.47,0:19:51.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能在这个家里说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.47,0:19:51.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,will not be mentioned in this household
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.50,0:19:53.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走吧  我来带你参观一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:53.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, let me show you around
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.50,0:19:54.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:54.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Larry
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.96,0:19:58.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在  小拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:58.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now, Larry
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.27,0:20:01.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为你献上晚餐时间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.27,0:20:01.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I present to you dinner time
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.30,0:20:02.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哒哒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:02.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ta-da
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.47,0:20:02.55,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(722,646)}小拉
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.55,0:20:04.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用餐愉快  小拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:04.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bon appétit, Larry
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.13,0:20:10.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.13,0:20:10.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.67,0:20:11.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等会再吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.67,0:20:11.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,maybe later
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.80,0:20:14.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就在这睡觉  小拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.80,0:20:14.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is where you sleep, Larry
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.51,0:20:22.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在那睡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.51,0:20:22.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's where I
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.85,0:20:30.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就让你睡那边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.85,0:20:30.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess you can sleep there
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.57,0:20:31.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就睡这下面好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.57,0:20:31.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll sleep down here
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.15,0:20:35.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安了  小拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.15,0:20:35.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, goodnight, Larry
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.47,0:20:43.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:43.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Larry
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.67,0:20:44.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想听笑话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.67,0:20:44.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Want to hear a joke?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.09,0:20:46.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗以前特别爱这条笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:46.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary used to love this one
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.57,0:20:50.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,船上的蜗牛叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.57,0:20:50.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you call a snail on a ship?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.57,0:20:52.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蜗手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.57,0:20:52.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A snailor
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.75,0:20:57.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没听懂吗  小拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:20:57.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it, Larry
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.96,0:20:58.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:20:58.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.78,0:20:59.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蜗手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.78,0:20:59.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a snailor
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.00,0:21:05.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  小拉跟小蜗区别太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.00,0:21:05.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gosh, Larry sure is different than Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.75,0:21:07.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗和小拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.75,0:21:07.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And Gary and Larry
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.05,0:21:10.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟小杰的区别非常大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.05,0:21:10.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are real different than Jerry
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.32,0:21:14.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  你为什么要离我而去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.32,0:21:14.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, why did you have to go?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.63,0:21:16.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.63,0:21:16.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.11,0:21:18.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:18.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,why?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.30,0:21:21.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.30,0:21:21.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, why?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.60,0:21:23.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.60,0:21:23.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.47,0:21:24.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.47,0:21:24.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.65,0:21:27.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.65,0:21:27.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.70,0:21:29.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:29.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.40,0:21:30.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.40,0:21:30.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.30,0:21:31.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请问可不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.30,0:21:31.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would it be all right
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.59,0:21:34.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我和小蜗在这洗衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.59,0:21:34.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if Gary and I did some laundry over here?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.99,0:21:35.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,洗衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.99,0:21:35.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Laundry?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.47,0:21:38.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们以前常常洗衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.47,0:21:38.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But we used to do laundry
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.70,0:21:39.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.70,0:21:39.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.56,0:21:40.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.56,0:21:40.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.63,0:21:42.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能借点肥皂用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.63,0:21:42.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could we borrow some soap?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.35,0:21:42.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肥皂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.35,0:21:42.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Soap?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.98,0:21:45.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们以前常常用肥皂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.98,0:21:45.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But we used to use soap
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.94,0:21:46.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.94,0:21:46.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you want
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.88,0:21:49.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,清香型还是耐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.88,0:21:49.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,fresh scent or heavy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.32,0:21:50.28,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(322,724)}清香型
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:50.28,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1120,770)}耐用型
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.27,0:21:50.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.27,0:21:50.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,du
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.29,0:21:51.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.29,0:21:51.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here it comes
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.07,0:21:57.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,耐用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.07,0:21:57.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Duty
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.07,0:21:57.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(710,920)}重 任
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.33,0:21:59.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.33,0:21:59.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.73,0:22:01.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你回来吧  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.73,0:22:01.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please come back, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.75,0:22:03.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.75,0:22:03.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please come home
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.89,0:22:07.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没了你我就废了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.89,0:22:07.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a wreck without you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.35,0:22:08.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.35,0:22:08.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.35,0:22:09.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果你回来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.35,0:22:09.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you come back
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.06,0:22:10.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就定一条不准定规矩的规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.06,0:22:10.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there will be a no-rules rule
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.65,0:22:12.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想什么时候玩什么东西都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.65,0:22:12.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can do whatever you want when you want
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.88,0:22:15.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想扒沙发可以使劲扒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.88,0:22:15.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you feel like ripping up the sofa, rip it up
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.35,0:22:16.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至于砂盆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.35,0:22:16.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the litter box?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.57,0:22:17.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用不着了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.57,0:22:17.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forget about it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.35,0:22:20.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全世界就是你的砂盆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.35,0:22:20.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The world is your litter box
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.86,0:22:21.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且你再也不用
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.86,0:22:21.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you don't have to
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.94,0:22:24.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等着我来喂你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.94,0:22:24.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wait around for me to feed you anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.01,0:22:26.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冰箱全天候随便开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.01,0:22:26.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,24-hour fridge access
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.57,0:22:30.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连碗都可以不用拿了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.57,0:22:30.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you don't even have to use a bowl
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.20,0:22:31.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道你有多喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.20,0:22:31.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know how much you like
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.71,0:22:33.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我珍贵的章鱼哥浮木雕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.71,0:22:33.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my prized driftwood carving of Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.84,0:22:36.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把它当抓板放心给你抓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.84,0:22:36.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, think of it as your own personal scratching post
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.32,0:22:37.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么样  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.32,0:22:37.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.37,0:22:39.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有不有趣  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.37,0:22:39.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Won't it be fun, Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.51,0:22:40.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太可悲了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.51,0:22:40.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How pathetic
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.92,0:22:41.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.92,0:22:41.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:22:44.22,0:22:46.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.22,0:22:46.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.25,0:22:48.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗现在只跟我走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.25,0:22:48.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but Gary's with me now
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.70,0:22:51.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你机会用完了  也失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.70,0:22:51.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You had your chance and you failed
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.47,0:22:54.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能再活在过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.47,0:22:54.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You have to stop living in the past
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.27,0:22:55.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,面对现实吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.27,0:22:55.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Face it, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.85,0:22:58.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你只会伤害到你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.85,0:22:58.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're only hurting yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.22,0:23:00.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是小蜗想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.22,0:23:00.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's what Gary wants
Dialogue: 1,0:23:00.44,0:23:03.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而小蜗想要的  就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.44,0:23:03.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and what Gary wants, is me
Dialogue: 1,0:23:03.70,0:23:04.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.70,0:23:04.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right, Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:10.32,0:23:13.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它只喜欢我的短裤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.32,0:23:13.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He only liked me for my shorts
Dialogue: 1,0:23:13.25,0:23:14.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.25,0:23:14.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:23:14.97,0:23:17.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗想要你口袋里的饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.97,0:23:17.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He wanted the cookie in your pocket
Dialogue: 1,0:23:27.00,0:23:29.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.00,0:23:29.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,G-G-Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:34.49,0:23:37.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  我就知道你不会抛弃我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.49,0:23:37.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, I knew you'd never leave me
Dialogue: 1,0:23:39.62,0:23:42.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们去遛遛吧  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.62,0:23:42.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go for a walk, pal
Dialogue: 1,0:23:44.22,0:23:45.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.22,0:23:45.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:46.30,0:23:50.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们先前经历的一切明明很特别
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.30,0:23:50.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought what we had was special
